race.comment: FROG MARCH (4) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (23.78) last time in a Mix 3/4 at Horsham. Solid record here winning two races. Should bounce back. PAW MADDOX (1) was below best at her last start when 6th at Horsham following a third place finish (22.27) at Warrnambool two back. Form here at the trip sound including two wins. One of the better chances. MAX PEARL (5) boasts a consistent overall record including six wins from 27 starts, but missed the frame latest when eighth (23.83) over 400m at Warragul. Goes well from this draw. Looks suited and expected to run well. BLAZIN' FRIES (6) must be respected at her pet distance.
